page_title: 'Using your data with Azure OpenAI Service'
page_description: Use this article to learn about using your data for better text generation in Azure OpenAI.
chunk_title: Use Azure OpenAI On Your Data securely
chunk_content: Use Azure OpenAI On Your Data securelyYou can use Azure OpenAI On Your Data securely by protecting data and resources with Microsoft Entra ID role-based access control, virtual networks, and private endpoints. You can also restrict the documents that can be used in responses for different users with Azure AI Search security filters. See Securely use Azure OpenAI On Your Data.
